3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper discusses the use of conventional learned features and compares them with the proposed exact blur measure. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with image processing and analysis. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with digital images and their analysis.
